ardjennersm_rmfk.htm |archive-date=14 April 2009  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JennerArchivesRCP\">{{cite web |url= http://www.aim25.ac.uk/cgi-bin/search2?coll_id=7135&inst_id=8 |title= JENNER, Edward (1749\u20131750) |author= [[Royal College of Physicians]] |work= AIM25 Archives }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"StGeorgesHistory\">{{cite web |url= http://www.stgeorges.nhs.uk/aboutourhistory.asp |title= Our History |author= [[St George's, University of London]] }}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Further reading==\n{{colbegin}}\n*[http://www.aim25.ac.uk/cgi-bin/search2?coll_id=7135&inst_id=8 Papers at the Royal College of Physicians]\n*[[John Baron (physician)|Baron, John]] M.D. F.R.S., \"The Life of Edward Jenner MD LLD FRS\", Henry Colburn, London, 1827.\n*Baron, John, \"The Life of Edward Jenner with illustrations of his doctrines and selections from his correspondence\". Two volumes. London 1838.\n*Edward Jenner, the man and his work. BMJ 1949 E Ashworth Underwood\n*Fisher, Richard B., \"Edward Jenner 1749\u20131823,\" Andre Deutsch, London, 1991.\n*{{Cite journal |author=Cartwright K |title=From Jenner to modern smallpox vaccines |journal=Occupational Medicine |volume=55 |issue=7 |page=563 |date=October 2005 |pmid=16251374 |doi=10.1093/occmed/kqi163|doi-access=free }}\n*{{Cite journal |author=Riedel S |title=Edward Jenner and the history of smallpox and vaccination |journal=Proceedings |volume=18 |issue=1 |pages=21\u201325 |date=January 2005 |pmid=16200144 |pmc=1200696 |doi=10.1080/08998280.2005.11928028}}\n*{{Cite journal |author=Tan SY |title=Edward Jenner (1749\u20131823): conqueror of smallpox |journal=Singapore Medical Journal |volume=45 |issue=11 |pages=507\u201308 |date=November 2004 |pmid=15510320 |url=http://www.sma.org.sg/smj/4511/4511ms1.pdf}}\n*{{Cite journal |author=van Oss CJ |title=Inoculation against smallpox as the precursor to vaccination |journal=Immunological Investigations |volume=29 |issue=4 |pages=443\u201346 |date=November 2000 |pmid=11130785}}\n*{{Cite journal |vauth